Package: PmagDiR
Type: Package
Title: Plot and assess reliability of paleomagnetic directions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Edoardo Dallanave
Maintainer: Edoardo Dallanave <edoardo@uni-bremen.de>
Description: The main functions of the package are:
    >plotting paleomagnetic directions, average and confidence cone
    >applying virtual-geomagneticpoles-based cut-off 
    >testing for antipodality
    >testing and correcting for paleomagnetic inclination shallowing
    >testing and (when possible) correcting for tectonic strain
Imports: 
    tidyverse(>= 2.0.0), matlib(>= 0.9.6), dplyr(>= 1.1.0), DescTools(>= 0.99.48),plyr(>= 1.8.9),shiny(>= 1.9.1),shinyWidgets(>= 0.8.6),shinyhelper(>= 0.3.2),DT(>= 0.33)
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
